(4) In addition to any penalty that may be imposed under subsection (3), any person responsible for the contamination or commingling of genetically modified crop with any non-genetically modified crop or cross-breeding between genetically modified livestock with non-genetically modified livestock shall compensate the person whose crop has been contaminated or livestock cross-bred as the case may be.
